list.name: Default Changelist
list.comment:
version 1.0 25-12-2019 - added into IndexRestController GET method by fire Id and iteration number. - added database layer with integration Spring JPA and supporting two individual DataSources: geometries(OSM data) and fires. - deleted redundant files from db and core package. - change logic for searching intersections agent ways with polygons in NetworkUtils.findIntersectionPoint.
In the next update will be implemented relief constraint for agents, new datasource for relief data, support external configuration application.properties

task.summary: version 1.0 Create a simple firefront with wind constraint.

version 0.5 10-12-2019 adding AgentMap to ru.nachos.utils package

version 0.5 16-12-2019 refactoring web layer: adding ResponseDataService, RequestDataService, RequestData, ResponseData, ResponseDataContainer etc. adding exception package inside core package for handling typical exceptions while processing calculation fire model

version 0.5 16-12-2019 adding into AgentChangePolygonHandlerImpl behavior for agents, which do not change polygon id. they checks their probability intersection with non-flam geometries.
